<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Oauth app</title>
    <style>
      * {
        font-family: sans-serif, "Roboto";
      }
      .header {
        max-width: 100vw;
        padding: 10px 0px;
        background-color: rgb(3, 73, 3);
        color: white;
      }
      .header ul {
        display: flex;
        width: 45%;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }
      ul li {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 10px;
        background-color: transparent;
        border-radius: 5px;
        border: none;
        font-size: 18px;
      }

      ul li:hover {
        background-color: rgba(158, 250, 158, 0.3);
      }
      .intro-text {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: green;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 20px;
        text-align: justify;
        color: black;
      }
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: white;
      }

      .body-content {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .body-content button {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 24px;
        background-color: green;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-radius: 50px;
      }

      .body-content div {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        width: 60%;
        background-color: rgba(138, 201, 138, 0.4);
        border: 1px solid green;
        border-radius: 50px;
        padding: 40px;
        margin-top: 40px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav class="header">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/auth/login">Sign up with OAuth</a></li>
        <li><a href="/auth/signup">Sign in with OAuth</a></li>
        <li><a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    <section class="body-content">
      <div>
        <h1 class="intro-text">Hello world OAUTH authentication code</h1>
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quidem
          doloribus voluptate quasi veritatis accusamus, sed minima voluptatibus
          laborum amet iusto. Inventore vitae fuga asperiores doloribus?
          Repellat deleniti distinctio dicta veritatis!
        </p>
        <button>Login with OAuth</button>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
